Bachelor’s Degree in a relevant field or equivalent professional experience;
Previous Capitol Hill, campaign or political experience strongly preferred;
Exceptionally strong writing, editing, and proofreading skills;
Previous on the record experience;
Ability to take photographs and write content for social media
Experience managing others and promoting professional development;
Deep understanding of print, broadcast, and online media and how to successfully create and leverage opportunities in each;
Strategic thinker, politically savvy, and ability to manage competing priorities and develop solutions under tight deadlines;
